@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@staffRole = STAFF
@staffId = staff-1
@managerRole = MANAGER
@managerId = manager-1
@barcode = 5012345678901

### Barcode lookup for POS scanners (STAFF+)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/barcode/{{barcode}}
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

### Existing fallback search endpoint still supported
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?q={{barcode}}
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

### Unknown barcode -> 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/barcode/0000000000000
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

### Manager can still use the endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/barcode/{{barcode}}
X-Staff-Role: {{managerRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{managerId}}
